about_short_description.short_description: Iceberg Data Lab offers financial companies with environmental data solutions to report and manage environmental impact.

product.name: Biodiversity Solutions
product.description: Tools to measure and manage financial institutions' impacts, dependencies, risks, and opportunities related to biodiversity.

product.name: Climate Solutions
product.description: A suite of solutions measuring carbon footprint, physical and transition risks, and alignment with the Paris agreement.

product.name: Regulatory Solutions
product.description: Solutions enabling compliance with environmental regulations and standards like TCFD and TNFD.

product.name: AI for Sustainable Finance (Barbatus)
product.description: A generative AI-powered ESG assistant aiding in data collection, research, benchmarking, and regulatory reporting.

product.name: Corporate Biodiversity Footprint (CBF)
product.description: A metric for assessing a company's impact on biodiversity in absolute and relative terms.

product.name: Dependency Score
product.description: Quantifies a company's reliance on ecosystem services across three categories.
